metadata.name: Jiggly
metadata.description:
Peputo, Discokid909, and Inferno are here to share to you this jiggly feeling. The community is like a disco. Colorful, diverse, and full of possibilities for all to explore. Everybody comes from different story and background, but there's also this sense of belonging that they all share as they dance together. Even Bub the devil sneaked in to join the fun. A new world is beginning.

Music by @Discokid909

_
All primary bidder and primary collector of this piece will get an NFT airdrop edition of 'Jiggly' jpeg with unlockable content (jpeg, 04:10 full track mp3). The collector will also be shared a link for the 15s mp4.
